casebody.data:
No. 632. Luigi Gandolfi et al., Petitioners, v. Alfredo C. Siegert, as surviving partner, etc. March 11, 1907. Mr. Edmund Wet-more and Mr. John Brooks Leavitt for petitioners. Mr. Edward B. Whitney for respondent.

Petition for' a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.
